## Record Format

```yaml
section: experience.record-format
title: Experience Record Format
status: active
owner: "{{ owner }}"
created_at: {{ created_at }}
updated_at: {{ updated_at }}
record_id_format: EXP-XXX
fields:
  - id
  - date
  - context
  - problem
  - impact
  - root_cause
  - corrective_action
  - preventive_action
  - status
  - owner
allowed_statuses:
  - open
  - mitigated
  - resolved
  - obsolete
tags: [format, experience, records]
```

Each experience record must use the following structure:

### EXP-XXX - Record title

```yaml
section: experience.EXP-XXX
id: EXP-XXX
title: Record title
date:
context:
problem:
impact:
root_cause:
corrective_action:
preventive_action:
status: open
owner: "{{ owner }}"
created_at:
updated_at:
```

Record narrative goes here.

[@ref: Related decision](decisions.md#decisions.DEC-XXX)
Related sprint URI: `sprints/SPR-YYYY-NN.md#sprint.SPR-YYYY-NN`
Related backlog item URI: `backlog/B-XXX.md#backlog.item.B-XXX`

